{
  "texts": [
    "We employed three kinds of search strings: (\"AI\" AND \"Epidemic modeling\"), (\"AI\" AND \"Modeling\" AND \"Infectious disease\"), and (\"AI\" AND \"Modeling\" AND \"Infectious agents\" AND \"Spreading\").",
    "Within each category, terms were linked by the Boolean operator \"OR.\"",
    "Restrictions on search functionality within IEEE Xplore and ACM Digital Library required multiple separate searches.",
    "We used the Polyglot tool 300 to translate search syntax across databases.",
    "Details of the search strings for each database can be found in Supplementary Appendix 2."
  ]
}